Different paths but same destination,
hence we're bound to meet.

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:47.639
Go.

00:02:48.120 --> 00:02:49.759
Light the incense for me.

00:02:49.759 --> 00:02:50.639
Yes, My Lord.

00:02:53.039 --> 00:02:54.560
I missed you so much.

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:55.599
Beauty.

00:02:56.479 --> 00:02:57.479
My Lord.

00:02:57.840 --> 00:02:58.599
Wait for me.

00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:00.840
I'm coming.

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:02.719
My Lord.

00:03:02.719 --> 00:03:03.520
Come on.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:09.680
Xiao Huaijin lives in luxury
and indulgence every day.

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:11.800
However, Prince Duan

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:14.319
seems almost too clean and simple.

00:03:16.520 --> 00:03:17.919
