00:10:19.639 --> 00:10:21.679
Xiao, the auspicious hour has arrived.

00:10:21.679 --> 00:10:23.200
We have to serve tea to Master.

00:10:23.200 --> 00:10:23.890
If we miss the hour,

00:10:23.900 --> 00:10:25.690
I won't get the chance
to pay respect to him.

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:29.240
